'''Blue Egg Lamppost''' is a [[Furniture#Other|non-themed]] piece of [[Crafting|craftable furniture]].

It can be [[Crafting|crafted]] using materials collected during the limited time [[Eggstravaganza]] event. The crafting recipe requires 5 [[Fishy Green Egg]]s, [[Sapphire]], [[Glass]], 2 [[Gold Ingot]]s, and [[Stone]]. Once collected it will be tracked in both the [[:Category:Dreamlight Valley Furniture Sets Collection|Dreamlight Valley Furniture Sets Collection]] and [[:Category:Dreamlight Valley Crafting Collection|Dreamlight Valley Crafting Collection]].

It can be positioned and placed using the [[Furniture menu]] inside the [[Inventory]]. Once it is placed in the world, the Player can '''Interact''' with the object to toggle the light on and off.

